{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b858d96637","title":"听取谷牧、余秋里汇报计划工作时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"75221e7754","index":0,"year":1965,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"b858d96637","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"余秋里","id":"a5ef5c1d16","type":"人物"},{"name":"谷牧","id":"b28bc58f9a","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d2cc1ccf94","type":"title","text":"听取谷牧、余秋里汇报计划工作时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8fc24042c2","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六五年一月谷牧、余秋里向毛泽东汇报计划工作，当讲到敢想敢干时）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25b00dcf5e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：要敢想敢干，不要乱来，破除迷信，不要破除科学。不要讲了半天，又是设计，又是试制，最后什么结果也没有。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"914bdfb97a","type":"paragraph","text":"（汇报到今年钢可以搞到口口方吨时）","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70420a697e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不是有一个消息吗，英国人听说我们搞调整、巩固，就害怕了。你不搞冒进，搞质量，搞品种、规格，他就怕了。数量慢慢上去，不要急。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e5b25e5cb","type":"paragraph","text":"（讲到口口建设时）","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"691a9a7e8d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：口口建设要抓紧，就是同帝国主义争时间，同修正主义争","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5214e01d7","type":"subtitle","text":"时间。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34626a5413","type":"paragraph","text":"（汇报到我们的技术要赶上和超过国际水平时）","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fbb432e4dd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：是的，我们要有.....管他什么国，管他什么弹，原子弹、氢弹，都要超过。我说过，原子弹响了，人类即使死一半，也还有一半。斯诺同我谈话，问我为什么不辟谣，我说不要辟谣。我只说过战争打起来人死一半，还有另外一半。有比我更厉害的，美国的一个影片形容得很厉害呀！赫鲁晓夫比我说的多得多嘛！他说有毁灭人类的武器，什么死光。我不是说中国，而是说全世界死三分之一，总而言之，死一半！口口建设，我们把钢铁、国防、机械、化工、石油、铁路基地都搞起来了，那时打起来就不怕了。搞不成，打起来怎么办？我们就用常规武器跟他们打。从前我们没飞机、大炮··..·又没有黄色炸药，还不是打赢了！打起来还可以继续建设，你打你的，我建设我的。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e31a2dc33","type":"paragraph","text":"（讲到设计一定要采用新技术时）","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d06895e436","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：设计要做比较，哪些花钱少，办事多，哪些花钱多，办事少。设计人员是在家里设计，还是到现场设计？我看了一万二千吨水压机设计的文章，有些设计经过一次、二次，甚至几百次的失败，不经过失败是不会成功的。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":477,"end":476}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1affa76e5b","type":"paragraph","text":"要敢想敢干，不要乱来，破除迷信，不要破除科学。不要讲了半天，又是设计，又是试制，最后什么结果也没有。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2c038298da","type":"paragraph","text":"不是有一个消息吗，英国人听说我们搞调整、巩固，就害怕了。你不搞冒进，搞质量，搞品种、规格，他就怕了。数量慢慢上去，不要急。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b858d96637","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2d688e0975","type":"paragraph","text":"敢干时）主席说：","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"b858d96637",